      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Kontroller:\r\nWASD - Hareket\r\nFare - Etrafa bak\r\nSol T\u0131k - esya
    al, kap\u0131lar\u0131 a\xE7, di\u011Fer \u015Feyler\nSa\u011F T\u0131k - Se\xE7ili
    esyay\u0131 kullan\r\nKayd\u0131rma Tekerle\u011Fi, 1, 2, 3 - esya se\xE7imini
    de\u011Fi\u015Ftir\r\nShift - Ko\u015F (h\u0131z bar\u0131na dikkat et!)\r\nBo\u015Fluk
    tu\u015Fu - Arkana bak ve Z\u0131pla!"
